Version Info

This version of our R Markdown file includes additional raincloud plots and standardized effect estimates that were not included in the previous version (20200921_Analysis.html/rmd). The corresponding .rmd-file (20201120_Analysis_extended.rmd) is not provided for copyright reasons. Please refer to the earlier version of the .rmd-file (20200921_Analysis.rmd) if you want to reproduce our statistical analyses (additional code for obtaining standardized estimates is printed in this .html-file) and refer to https://micahallen.org/2018/03/15/introducing-raincloud-plots/ for code on raincloud plots.
